item.immersive_aircraft.rotary_cannon.de: Póca gastaigh le gunpowder atá ag rith.
item.immersive_aircraft.bomb_bay.descrip: Droichid TNT, nach scriosann blocanna ach déan maith damáiste.
item.immersive_aircraft.heavy_crossbow.d: Croisbhóthar trom le pasáige d'áit, teastaíonn laige.
item.immersive_aircraft.airship.descript: Airships may not be the fastest vehicle, but they sure are easy to maneuver.
item.immersive_aircraft.cargo_airship.de: Mhall ionsabail agus ag ithe breosla ach aCarry an stór ar fad.
item.immersive_aircraft.warship.descript: Dún forta, mall ach armáilte go trom.
item.immersive_aircraft.biplane.descript: Tapa agus rather a spraoi. Déan cinnte go bhfuil do rún leordhóthan.
item.immersive_aircraft.gyrodyne.descrip: Who needs an engine if one could power the aircraft with pure brawn? Give it a good push and off it flies!
item.immersive_aircraft.quadrocopter.des: A masterwork of engineering! 4 rotors strapped to some bamboo. Perfect for building, and that's about it.
immersive_aircraft.gyrodyne_target_reach: Sceideal cuaille íostéite, réidh le haghaidh éirí!
immersive_aircraft.invalid_dimension: Ní oibríonn an t-aerárthach seo sa diméoin seo.
immersive_aircraft.fat.out: Tá tú rómhór ocrach chun eitilt!
option.immersive_aircraft.separateCamera: Gnéas camara ar leith i aerlong.
option.immersive_aircraft.useThirdPerson: Deault le camara tríú duille i aerlong.
option.immersive_aircraft.repairExhausti: Tuirse an imreora in aghaidh an chliceáil.
option.immersive_aircraft.useCustomKeybi: Úsáidilt eochairchórais il, d'fhéadfadh gafa a chur ar chomhoibriún áirithe.

option.immersive_aircraft.preventKillThr: Ní mharóidh sé an imreoir ar chras.
option.immersive_aircraft.damagePerHealt: Luachanna níos airde a dhéanann na heitseoirí níos durable.

option.immersive_aircraft.regenerateHeal: Athghintear sláinte go huathoibríoch gach tacar ama a tugadh, ag simpliú iompar vanilla.
option.immersive_aircraft.requireShiftFo: Ná déan deisiú nuair a bhíonn tú ag coinneáil shift, ach téigh isteach sa charr.
immersive_aircraft.tooltip.no_target: Caithfear é a chur le chéile ar an talamh!
